title: UTS links students with global startups (UTS - University of Technology, Sydney)
text: ( Source : UTS - University of Technology, Sydney ) UTS is launching a pilot program to connect future leaders with entrepreneurs from around the world, starting with a one-day international entrepreneurs networking event on Friday 23 October .
